- Log history length before/after each prune
- Log which messages were removed (content preview, not full)
- Log token counts if token-based truncation
- Log PASS/FAIL for each test

## Coverage Requirements
- All truncation paths (message-based, token-based)
- System message preservation
- Edge cases (empty, single, null content)
- Multi-session isolation

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] Message-based truncation works at limit
- [ ] System message always preserved at index 0
- [ ] Token-based truncation keeps under limit
- [ ] Recent messages preferred over old
